This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of Computer Security and Cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also discusses network threats and datasets, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
